.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, soy-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian, manager, software-developer
4 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, canasta, domino
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
2. the librarian is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the manager##3
4. the librarian is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the fisherman##1
6. the person playing domino is on the right of the librarian##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the librarian##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | 7up                | soy-milk  | almond-milk | juice   |
| Job           | software-developer | librarian | fisherman   | manager |
| Game   | mah-jongg         | chess     | domino     | canasta |

