.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, magic-tricks, skydiving
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indian, indonesian, japanese
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, december, january, march
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person who's birthday is in may##2
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the japanese is between the person who's birthday is in may and the australian##2
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
8. the indian is in an even position##4
9. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | magic-tricks | dancing  | skydiving  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | indian       | japanese | australian |
| Birthday         | january   | may      | march | december       |

