.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, mirinda, tea
4 different pets are kept: hamster, frog, guinea-pig, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car, snowmobile
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the owner of the hamster is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person drinking milk is between the person driving the bike and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
6. the person driving the airplane is the owner of the snake##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | mirinda    | milk     | cola    | tea        |
| Pet       | guinea-pig   | hamster | frog | snake |
| Transport   | snowmobile | car      | bike    | airplane   |

