4. the person who's hobby is reading is the fan of metal##1
5. the italian is on the right of the colombian##1
6. the fan of punk is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the fan of disco##1
8. the indian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
